{
  "stem": "6736.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was playing music-- [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Mother, Mother, I will return.' When they took away the children, there was a lot of screaming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Throughout the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939, or beginning of '40, Oskar Schindler received, as a Jewish enterprise, received Emalia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was immediately different than the other Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Normally, the Germans will take away the Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people will have, next to the store, a nice apartment or a nice house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will take that away and chase the Jew out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- because, maybe, it was a factory-- he said, I don't know how to run pots and pans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he took in the Jewish people to run it for him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he immediately made a 50-50 deal. 50% of the goods that there were made was going to the German government, and 50% was sold on the market-- black market.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the black market was also 50-50. 25-- he took 50% for himself, so he will have to bribe people to run parties.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And 50% he will leave  it in the Jewish hands, and they will buy food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the beginning, in the Emalia was working Christians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But because of being able to get a Kennkarte-- Kennkarte, that's a special paper to go to the camp, to the, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had to have papers that you work in the Emalia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Like I said before, German enterprises.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So people will be in the ghetto, and from the ghetto they will go out to the Emalia to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People will pay money, gold, silver, whatever they had-- could lay a hand on them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even they will assign houses for the future, those red houses-- to get him papers that he works in Emalia.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
